	<section class="parameters">
		<h2>Parameters</h2>
		<dl>
									<dt>$args</dt>
						<dd>
				<p class="desc">
										<span class="type">(<span class="array">array</span>)</span>
															<span class="required">(Optional)</span>
															<span class="description">The search arguments. Optional. - errors      mixed  True to return themes with errors, false to return themes without errors, null                      to return all themes. Defaults to false. - allowed     mixed  (Multisite) True to return only allowed themes for a site. False to return only                      disallowed themes for a site. 'site' to return only site-allowed themes. 'network'                      to return only network-allowed themes. Null to return all themes. Defaults to null. - blog_id     int    (Multisite) The blog ID used to calculate which themes are allowed. Defaults to 0,                      synonymous for the current blog.</span>
									</p>
								<p class="default">Default value: array()</p>
